Bojar Nishani o siwkay 9 bolad 29 demiad, Bojar Nishani, o misingkiway. 1966 a mihcan nalecohan. o tabakiay a tapang no kanatal (congtong) no Albania ayza sa ci Bojar Nishani, micakat a demiad sa i 2012 a mihcan 7 bolad 24 demiad. o solit no zoma a kamo maala ciniza i 2017.7 o tapang no kanatal, i sinkiw kya tapang no kanatal, maala 73 paya' i labo' no 140. o solit no Amilika: Bojar Nishani is an Albanian politician who was President of Albaniafrom 24 Joly 2012 to 24 Joly 2017. o solit no Lipon: . malalitin to ihekalay ato zomaay a natinengan: 布亞爾·法伊克·尼沙尼 Bojar Nishani ブヤル・ファイク・ニシャニ
